---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Teddy Travels">
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">A personal archive by Luke Tedford</p>
    <h1>Teddy Travels</h1>
    <p>
      Mountains, road trips, surf, work seasons, study abroad, gear notes,
      photos, and whatever else happens outside.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <h2>What this is</h2>
    <p>
      This site is my digital scrapbook: part trip report collection, part photo
      archive, part gear notebook, and part record of the places I’ve been and
      the objectives I’m working toward.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card-grid">
    <article class="card feature-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Routes, peaks, trails</p>
      <h2>Outdoors</h2>
      <p>
        Climbing, hiking, backpacking, scrambling, snow climbs, trail runs, and
        short expedition reports.
      </p>
      <a href="/outdoors">Explore outdoor reports →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card feature-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Longer stories</p>
      <h2>Trips</h2>
      <p>
        Road trips, surf trips, work seasons, study abroad, international
        backpacking, and other nonstandard chapters.
      </p>
      <a href="/trips">Read travel stories →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card feature-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Images from the road</p>
      <h2>Photos</h2>
      <p>
        Favorite shots from trails, peaks, campsites, coastlines, cities, and
        strange roads.
      </p>
      <a href="/photos">View gallery →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card feature-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Future missions</p>
      <h2>Objectives</h2>
      <p>
        Peaks, routes, countries, trails, and ideas I’m chasing.
      </p>
      <a href="/objectives">See objectives →</a>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="quote-block">
    <p>
      “A place to keep the stories before they turn into half-remembered camera
      roll fragments.”
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>